id: pm-3z0k
title: "Portable integrity attestation: export a detached hash-chain proof bundle and verify it standalone, so third parties can confirm the recorded history was never altered"
description: ""
type: Feature
status: open
priority: 3
tags[3]: governance,history,immutable-record
