acceptance_criteria: "attest export produces a documented, versioned bundle covering all item and workspace history streams with a workspace rollup digest; verify against a bundle detects any post-export stream rewrite and names the diverged streams; verify runs read-only with no locks and works on a bare clone; compact/redact/repair produce lineage-visible digest transitions (tested); SDK exposes export/verify primitives with reference docs; bundle stays small (KBs, independent of workspace size beyond stream count)"
